{"tid":1060154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲專利局2018申請排名　西門子第一華為第二","createTime":"2019-03-13T14:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T03:06:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae386eac04a21fb870e9c2467d1cde22a70ccf6","tid":1060154,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190313/s00005/922826b891e3327b62c42460e7aef3cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190313%2Fs00005%2F922826b891e3327b62c42460e7aef3cd.jpg&h=5986c23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總部位於德國的歐洲專利局（European Patent Office），今日公布2018年專利申請的統計數據。當中申請專利最多的企業，首位是德國電子巨頭西門子，去年共申請2493項專利；2017年時同一統計居首的內地通訊設備製造商華為，今次則比西門子少申請8項專利居次位。<br />\n<br />\n其餘排名前10的企業，依次為韓國三星、韓國LG、美國聯合技術公司、荷蘭飛利浦、美國高通、瑞典愛立信、美國通用電氣和德國Bosch。<br />\n<br />\n若依範疇分類，去年在歐洲專利局申請的專利中，最多的是醫療技術專利，共有13795項，較2017年上升5%；其次是通訊科技專利，共11940項，較2017年上升0.7%。<br />\n<br />\n從專利來源地來看，申請專利最多的是美國，佔整體25%，其餘排名前10的國家分別是德國、日本、法國、中國、瑞士、韓國、荷蘭、英國和意大利。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社/歐洲專利局官網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190313/s00005/1552446505787/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E5%B1%802018%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D-%E8%A5%BF%E9%96%80%E5%AD%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190313%2Fs00005%2F1552446505787%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B1%25802018%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%2590%258D-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=21160e3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190313%2Fs00005%2F1552446505787%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B1%25802018%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%2590%258D-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C&h=4efd9656\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190313/s00005/1552446505787/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9%E5%B1%802018%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D-%E8%A5%BF%E9%96%80%E5%AD%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C</a>"},{"pid":"4e6e46f47a7db13759db898f24082b2af76be09a","tid":1060154,"uid":181666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"任正非好癲"},{"pid":"c01dc96f0852628c5aa39e5cba45903882ea30fd","tid":1060154,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6e46f47a7db13759db898f24082b2af76be09a","tid":1060154,"uid":181666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"任正非好癲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"<del>任正非好癲</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共好顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f933728f16b33da722b469c47946bf1d2220e0","tid":1060154,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}